### Sanos y Salvos - Coleccion API completa
### Formato VS Code REST Client (extension humao.rest-client)
### Equipo: Yamil Apablaza, Alvaro Del Canto, Santiago Vargas

@bff = http://localhost:5000/api
@auth_service = http://localhost:8001
@user_service = http://localhost:8002
@geo_service = http://localhost:8003/api
@chat_service = http://localhost:8004
@match_service = http://localhost:8005
@media_service = http://localhost:8006
@notif_service = http://localhost:8007

### ============================================================
### AUTH SERVICE (puerto 8001)
### ============================================================

### Login (obtener tokens JWT)
# @name login
POST {{auth_service}}/api/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Refresh token
POST {{auth_service}}/api/token/refresh/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "{{login.response.body.refresh}}"
}

### Verificar token
POST {{auth_service}}/api/token/verify/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{login.response.body.access}}"
}

### ============================================================
### USER SERVICE (puerto 8002)
### ============================================================

### Registrar usuario
POST {{user_service}}/api/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "full_name": "Alice Perez",
  "rut": "17.685.439-5",
  "phone": "+56987654321",
  "commune": "Providencia",
  "address": "Av. Siempre Viva 742",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Listar usuarios
GET {{user_service}}/api/users/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access}}

### Detalle de usuario por ID
GET {{user_service}}/api/users/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access}}

### Actualizar usuario
PATCH {{user_service}}/api/users/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+56912345678"
}

### ============================================================
### GEO SERVICE (puerto 8003)
### ============================================================

### Listar todas las ubicaciones (paginado DRF)
GET {{geo_service}}/ubicaciones/

### Listar con filtros
GET {{geo_service}}/ubicaciones/?tipo_animal=perro&tipo_reporte=perdido

### Crear reporte (con URL de imagen desde MediaService)
POST {{geo_service}}/ubicaciones/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reporte_id": "rep_001",
  "pet_id": "pet_001",
  "usuario_id": 1,
  "latitud": -33.4569,
  "longitud": -70.6483,
  "tipo_reporte": "perdido",
  "tipo_animal": "perro",
  "raza_probable": "Labrador",
  "color": "Negro",
  "titulo": "Perdi a Toby cerca del parque",
  "descripcion": "Collar azul, microchip ABC123",
  "fecha_reporte": "2026-06-17T10:00:00Z",
  "imagen_url": "http://localhost:8006/media/pets_uploaded/abc.jpg"
}

### Buscar reportes cercanos (10km a la redonda)
POST {{geo_service}}/ubicaciones/buscar_cercanos/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitud": -33.4569,
  "longitud": -70.6483,
  "radio_km": 10,
  "tipo_reporte": "ambos"
}

### Obtener reportes cercanos a un reporte especifico (tipo opuesto)
GET {{geo_service}}/ubicaciones/1/obtener_cercanos/?radio=20

### Estadisticas geograficas
POST {{geo_service}}/ubicaciones/stats_geografico/

### ============================================================
### MATCH SERVICE (puerto 8005) - via BFF (proxy)
### ============================================================

### Analizar imagen con Gemini (multipart) - via BFF
POST {{bff}}/match/analyze
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="reporte_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pet_type"

perro
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="toby.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./toby.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### ============================================================
### MEDIA SERVICE (puerto 8006) - via BFF (proxy)
### ============================================================

### Upload de imagen de mascota
POST {{bff}}/media/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="toby.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./toby.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Toby el labrador
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Listar imagenes subidas
GET {{media_service}}/api/images/

### ============================================================
### NOTIFICATION SERVICE (puerto 8007) - via BFF
### ============================================================

### Listar notificaciones del usuario
GET {{bff}}/notifications/?user_id=1

### Marcar notificacion como leida
POST {{bff}}/notifications/5/mark-read

### Disparar notificacion de match (BFF -> NotificationService)
POST {{bff}}/notifications/trigger-match
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "user_email": "alice@example.com",
  "match_id": 99,
  "pet_name": "Toby"
}

### ============================================================
### CHAT SERVICE (puerto 8004) - via BFF
### ============================================================

### Config WS del chat (URL del WebSocket)
GET {{bff}}/chat/config

### Validar acceso a sala
GET {{bff}}/chat/room/perros-perdidos

### WebSocket (no se puede via REST Client, usar wscat o el frontend):
###   ws://localhost:8004/ws/chat/perros-perdidos/

### ============================================================
### BFF - SALUD Y AUTH
### ============================================================

### Health check del BFF
GET {{bff}}/health

### Login via BFF (stub)
POST {{bff}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Admin login (admin/admin para dev)
POST {{bff}}/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Dashboard admin (requiere token admin)
GET {{bff}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer admin-token-123
